document.discussion_title: CARLOS GOMEZ A KEDA DESIGNA PA ASIGNASHON
document.topic_text: Pa abona EXTRA.CW klik riba e link aki. 2016-08-11 / Mundu Deportivo Print CARLOS GOMEZ A KEDA DESIGNA PA ASIGNASHON HOUSTON.- Den un moveshon ku tòg hopi no a spera, e ekipo di Houston Astros a designá e outfielder Carlos Gomez pa asignashon. Esaki ta nifiká ku nan a kita Gomez for dirosterdi40Ieekipotin awor 10 dia pa sea kambi’é, lag’é den libertat òf mand’é Liga Menor.
